   <body>
      <context>You can reject a pending user account registration for pending user requests.</context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click <uicontrol>Administration</uicontrol>.




</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>ADMINISTRATION</uicontrol> page is displayed.
</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol>User Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol>Pending Registrations</uicontrol>.

</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>PENDING REGISTRATIONS LIST</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the required user registration request to reject.

</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Reject</uicontrol>.
</p>
            <p>A confirmation message is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
